  "principle": "AI operations as a first-class lane: anomaly detection, eval-gated automation signals, injection red-team evidence, and agent reliability witnesses. AIOps does not own model training (MLOps / gtcx-os/platform/intelligence); it operates fleet AI reliability and agent conduct surfaces.",
  "threePlanes": {
    "engineering": { "owner": "product-repo", "pmLeads": true, "blocksIRDefault": false },
    "aiops": {
